Package: xad
Type: Package
Title: High-Performance Automatic Differentiation for R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("Angel", "Robles", email = "alrobles@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("XAD Contributors", role = "ctb", comment = "Authors of the underlying XAD C++ library"))
Description: Provides R bindings to the high-performance XAD automatic
    differentiation library. Supports both forward and adjoint (reverse) mode
    automatic differentiation with expression templates and tape-based recording.
    Designed for zero-copy integration with R memory through column-major layouts.
License: AGPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++17, CMake (>= 3.15)
URL: https://github.com/alrobles/xad-r
BugReports: https://github.com/alrobles/xad-r/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.0.0
